_:Ndbab8856402b4a369a866f38860b93d2 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Paul joined the Nuclear Decommissioning Authority in June 2016 from Rolls Royce, where he held a number of senior positions including Director of Communications and Marketing for the Land and Sea Division, which incorporated the Marine, Nuclear and Power Systems businesses.</p>\n\n<p>Prior to that, he was Group Communications Director for BNFL. Paul has a degree in Physics.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
